headline: Costco Stock Thrives When Other Stocks Are Down. Is Now the Time to Buy?
summary: Costco makes money on its memberships instead of marking up prices, and shoppers love it when they're careful about spending.  Costco stock has a premium price tag.  The market just can't get enough of Costco Wholesale (NASDAQ: COST) stock, and economic volatility is only helping.
